profile.primary_concern: accessing healthcare resources while being homeless

context: As a young man experiencing homelessness, you may feel overwhelmed by daily survival challenges. Finding stable housing and basic needs often overshadows health concerns, making it difficult to prioritize or access PrEP. Stigma around your situation can also fuel fear and uncertainty about seeking help.
